# SVG Group API: Always restart yourself

When you make changes that affect the SVG Group API (e.g. in `web-dashboard/svg-group-api/`), **restart the SVG Group API yourself**. Do not ask the user to restart.

Run in the background from repo root:

```bash
cd web-dashboard/svg-group-api && python app.py
```

Use `is_background: true`. Do not say "please restart the SVG Group API" or "you may need to restart"â€”just run the command.
